quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  30,25,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko …óin: nde kammu ngun e leydi ndin daroto e yamiroore Makko. Refti si O noddii on noddaandu ka leydi, e jaka onon hi…óon yalta (e genaale mon)"
  30,26,"Hino woodani (laamagol, e tagugol e toppitagol) …ìen won…ìe ka kammuuli e ka leydi: kala ma…ì…ìe ko …óoftii…ìe Mo"
  30,27,"Ko Kanko woni fu…ó…óu…óo tagu ngun, refti O ruttita ngu; ko …óum …ìuri newanaande Mo. Hino woodani sifa …ìur…óo toowude ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Ko Kanko woni on Foolu…óo, √ëee√±u…óo on"
  30,28,"O piyanii on misal immorde e ko'e-mon: hara no woodani on e …ìen …ìe jeyru…óon √±aame mon, immorde e kafidal e kon ko Men arsiki on, hara hi…óon fota e …óum, hi…óon hulira …ìe wano hulirton ko'e-mon? Ko woni nii Men fensitirta Aayeeje …óen, wonannde yim…ìe haqqiloo…ìe"
  30,29,"Si ko woni, too√±u…ìe …ìen jokkirii belee…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen ko aldaa e ganndal. Ko hommbo fewnata mo Alla majjini? Alanaa …ìe walloo…ìe"
  30,30,"Fewtinir yeeso maa ngon e diina kan √±ii…ìugol [e mun]. [∆äum] ko tagu Alla ngu O tagiri yim…ìe …ìen e mun - wa…ótitugol alaa e tagu Alla ngun -. Ko …óum woni diina focciika kan; kono …ìur…ìe …óuu…óude e yim…ìe …ìen anndaa"
  30,31,"Hara ko on ruttotoo…ìe e Makko; hulon Mo, √±innon julde nden, wata on jeye e sirkoo…ìe …ìen"
  30,32,"(wano) …ìeya senndunoo…ìe diina mun kan, …ìe woni pecce-pecce, kala fedde no weltora ko woni ka mun kon"
